# AVAudioVoiceProcessingOtherAudioDuckingConfiguration.Level.mid

**Case**

Applies medium ducking to other audio.

## Declaration

```swift
case mid
```

## Ducking levels

- **AVAudioVoiceProcessingOtherAudioDuckingConfiguration.Level.default**: The default ducking level for typical voice chat.
- **AVAudioVoiceProcessingOtherAudioDuckingConfiguration.Level.max**: Applies maximum ducking to other audio.
- **AVAudioVoiceProcessingOtherAudioDuckingConfiguration.Level.min**: Applies minimum ducking to other audio.
